                                <h4 class="text-vignette font-weight-bold justify-content-center text-center">Paths through the illustrations of the “Quarantana”</h4>
                                <div class="testo3 align-items-center">
                                    <p>The <a href="https://dlrc.ficlit.unibo.it/s/lib/faceted-browse/7" target="_blank">VEDO MANZONI</b></a> 
                                        project proposes a journey through the illustrations that Manzoni intended 
                                        to accompany the reading of the final version of the novel.</p>

